{"tid":342233,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩人會仆街得過 唔安慰你仲踩你一腳嘅人","createTime":"2017-07-31T12:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T11:19:10.000Z","uid":68008,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"801764bb952d6d2e96713a91e47532aaad460106","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"人地搵得你傾訴就代表佢信任你、肯同你交心架啦<br />\n屌你老母唔安慰都算 仲要踩多人兩腳 俾說話人聽 知唔知人地會幾難受？<br />\n本來已經好差嘅心情即刻跌到落谷底 究竟體諒一個唔開心嘅人係咪好難？<br />\n由佢自己講想講嘅野 你坐係隔離認真聽已經好足夠<br />\n<br />\n但係仍然會踩鳩你、未聽就批評你嘅人 只係個賤到冇撚得再賤嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e5eba946b21a2100c83de8a51291f9e59074cd","tid":342233,"uid":44775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:26:53.000Z","msg":"你確定佢係你朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce38d03eadc86113c91c2cb8a0ac2d81a7d1a36c","tid":342233,"uid":33896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:29:08.000Z","msg":"你確定你唔係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d7d84ea15efdfa2edda44003986d71bb242f11","tid":342233,"uid":49291,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"就係當你朋友，先鬧醒你。"},{"pid":"9c070805ab6652891d83e1c1b52abc253593cb12","tid":342233,"uid":105598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"我答 <br />\n就係踩你兩腳"},{"pid":"d152daac26b01d96dca5c4da54a0359b02919daf","tid":342233,"uid":122514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"我明 講一句駁十句 總之係你錯<br />\n真係好煩 明明安慰一句就會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53efbbfd7f5cef4cebf7ec0789f44370a3d61eb6","tid":342233,"uid":30751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"屌醒你咋on9"},{"pid":"a7f5dc2f37eb11530ffa347a416ce9d2db60f4db","tid":342233,"uid":127185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:44:13.000Z","msg":"屌鳩佢囉唔gur"},{"pid":"e61a03538767fa07875c02d220f1e0ad2eb142a1","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你確定佢係你朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我確定佢係我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd0ca195641f486ea83a6ef62e9d5abacf7724c","tid":342233,"uid":6337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你確定佢係你朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我確定佢係我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我男朋友都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ea30654ec57b16d06a5d174c23d2e1c514d348","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你確定你唔係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩都未講就踩我幾十腳 何況我只係想分享下自己感受姐<br />\n咁都有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf3d2817782b445d84c77dd0007cb54b6b0d2b3","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我答 <br />\n就係踩你兩腳</blockquote><br />\n你的資訊很有用"},{"pid":"2db0648c09fd6a249780a25935b43b75842250ad","tid":342233,"uid":112623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"Ex就係咁 頂唔順分咗手"},{"pid":"dfc614f64f4cb2b8d83f7468ee0adfe462e6ab82","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明 講一句駁十句 總之係你錯<br />\n真係好煩 明明安慰一句就會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算唔安慰 都起碼俾我發洩下 我講完想講嘅野咪收皮囉<br />\n一句都未聽就屌鳩我 唔講仲以為我殺左佢全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01daeef188bb7a2b6f9a8c2c4a3efce02e9c763","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌鳩佢囉唔gur</blockquote><br />\n屌完上黎取下暖姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57568003edf4e5c4b5373af92e9bd73eba9f44b","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ex就係咁 頂唔順分咗手</blockquote><br />\n祝你唔會再遇到呢啲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd6ee23be95719effcf392515ffc59aa21c7b08","tid":342233,"uid":89316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:18:53.000Z","msg":"係friend嘅實踩兩句先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72bed1f10ce3846f649c3361930092a43c05107","tid":342233,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:16:49.000Z","msg":"有咩唔開心講出黎俾我開心下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea1ceb62ff3a45c72b07c8ee45d400aefc86e3c","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩唔開心講出黎俾我開心下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想搵個人呻下姐 點知得唔到安慰仲要有反效果<br />\n我係好少叫春個類人黎 最近真係有啲好大嘅煩惱 先想搵佢呻下開解下我<br />\n都未講煩緊啲咩已經俾人屌鑊金 我都唔知講咩好<br />\n依家煩上加煩啊救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f279314127289c37d1e6f40fd262927e455d4b","tid":342233,"uid":35124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"雖然我知樓主可能唔係咁既意思 但係<br />\n咩都話晒你岩 「食屎好丫 我支持你食屎」咁好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585364cdea2235ea52334225b9d9657f6fa773a2","tid":342233,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d06c62c87a7ba24a1154eacc8a217367094e46","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然我知樓主可能唔係咁既意思 但係<br />\n咩都話晒你岩 「食屎好丫 我支持你食屎」咁好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係要人咩都話哂我啱 但係至少唔應該未聽就去批評掛⋯⋯ <br />\n我都未講件事 就鬧我話係我錯 直程聽都唔聽<br />\n搵得人訴苦就係想聽啲鼓勵/支持嘅說話同聽人意見架啦<br />\n但係依家我苦又訴唔到 仲要俾人話返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887c5b6eb4afdbcd5a2b8e1188ce09b4ed1f1d21","tid":342233,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"其實我自己都係mean嗰type<br />\n通常有人呻我會過份理性咁同佢分析事件而唔記得左鳩噏啲『帽事嘅』『係佢衰啦』之類嘅廢話去安撫人<br />\n因為我覺得有啲咩事唔順心就去解決左佢最實際<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396ea32f98eebe280e47a9c02ba7414d055af9f8","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我自己都係mean嗰type<br />\n通常有人呻我會過份理性咁同佢分析事件而唔記得左鳩噏啲『帽事嘅』『係佢衰啦』之類嘅廢話去安撫人<br />\n因為我覺得有啲咩事唔順心就去解決左佢最實際<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954eac6b47fca9236f4a64902c432f8d3114d4c8","tid":342233,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"抱歉，理性解決問題最實際<br />\n不過我認為安慰可以算係幫助到人去變番理性嘅一個手段"},{"pid":"336cc8df4daf6bd6b04fefc34baf7c07c59e1fa1","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抱歉，理性解決問題最實際<br />\n不過我認為安慰可以算係幫助到人去變番理性嘅一個手段</blockquote><br />\n兩句都認同 <br />\n當一個人未平復到心情 又點去理性咁思考解決方法<br />\n而我個一刻想要嘅就係得到安撫 再去諗方法<br />\n所以無論點俾意見我 我都唔會聽得入耳住"},{"pid":"7b58a480a7683b9310dba7c1dcb6e7615c9cdff1","tid":342233,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:05:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抱歉，理性解決問題最實際<br />\n不過我認為安慰可以算係幫助到人去變番理性嘅一個手段</blockquote><br />\n兩句都認同 <br />\n當一個人未平復到心情 又點去理性咁思考解決方法<br />\n而我個一刻想要嘅就係得到安撫 再去諗方法<br />\n所以無論點俾意見我 我都唔會聽得入耳住</blockquote><br />\n學識捨棄一d冇用嘅情緒，可以幫到你更理性思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我自己都係咁，基本上已經可以冇咩不良情緒"},{"pid":"3bfd19f53fe18be4156d10affd0a248e58fae246","tid":342233,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:09:13.000Z","msg":"睇下佢係想屌醒你定純粹踩你<br />\n踩就真心咪再來往<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786c10c73c6934184f2ca414f996bbd04acdfa0f","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>抱歉，理性解決問題最實際<br />\n不過我認為安慰可以算係幫助到人去變番理性嘅一個手段</blockquote><br />\n兩句都認同 <br />\n當一個人未平復到心情 又點去理性咁思考解決方法<br />\n而我個一刻想要嘅就係得到安撫 再去諗方法<br />\n所以無論點俾意見我 我都唔會聽得入耳住</blockquote><br />\n學識捨棄一d冇用嘅情緒，可以幫到你更理性思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我自己都係咁，基本上已經可以冇咩不良情緒</blockquote><br />\n我淨係識收埋自己啲情緒 好怕叫春會煩到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同時亦都唔想俾人發現自己嘅情緒 寧願自己一個唔開心 頹完就冇事<br />\n所以今次都真係鼓起勇氣同佢訴苦 因為真係俾件事困擾左好耐 點知就搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3537ae240f87e0f3a82554454559092c0448fe0","tid":342233,"uid":68008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T19:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下佢係想屌醒你定純粹踩你<br />\n踩就真心咪再來往<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重點係佢都未聽我講就話我平常呢樣唔啱 個樣錯<br />\n但係佢鬧嘅野同我想講件事係冇相關<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5efbf19213d188d4d8abf3ec52c21ede5596b